    "synopsis": "On the dust-blown Imperial world of Nurth, an Imperial Army officer named Peto Soneka is fighting a colonial counter-insurgency that will not end. Strange men in green and gold — the Alpha Legion — arrive late and seem to know more about the war than the men fighting it. Beyond the battlefield, the perfumed xenos cabal known only as the Cabal walks the spy John Grammaticus through prophecy: the war to come, they tell him, ends only one way, and to save the human species the species must lose. By the close, the brothers who lead the Alpha Legion — primarchs whose number history will misremember — have made the most cynical bet in the Heresy.",
